  <brief_title>Aldara for the Treatment of Large and/or Multiple sBCC</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Tolerance of Imiquimod 5% Cream for the Treatment of a Large and/or Multiple Superficial Basal Cell Carcinoma.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
